title: Morgantown Campus Self-Reported Cases by Day
description: The following positive cases were self-reported to the University by students, faculty and staff who were tested outside the University testing process. Positive cases must be reported to WVU: Students should notify the WVU CARE Team, and employees should notify WVU Medical Management.Self-reported cases are listed on the date they were reported to WVU, not the date the cases were tested.
